page.title: 16RIBBON DEVELOPMENT
page.content: NORTH OF A594 A variety of urban development exists along the main road from Maryport to Dearham. Ther are 14 large Victorian houses,9 early C20 bungalows,2 post war detached houses and 1 post war bungalow.Ther is a garage and 1 working farm.(pastoral) NY0436 There are 2 large detached houses and a market garden and 2 farms. NY0434 This is pasture land used for grazing and silage with 2 fields of barley and 1 of vegetables.There are 2 dismantled tramways for carrying coal to Maryport docks.The community of Woodside has 2 farmhouses and a farm workers bungalow and several farm buildings.
